    Number: LI
---
Who is that man,
whom all despise?
His poor, stupid heart
gone silly with anger,
meat-eye drunk blind.
When he sees a Buddha, he doesn't bow ...
When he sees a monk, he gives no alms ...
The butcher hacks out the biggest cuts,
but beyond that, he has no other talent ...
